headline: Fiserv and ADP Team Up to Empower Small Business Success
summary: MILWAUKEE & ROSELAND, N.J., November 19, 2024--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, and ADP® (Nasdaq: ADP), a leading global technology company providing human capital management (HCM) solutions, today announced a strategic partnership that brings together Fiserv’s preeminent small business solutions, including Clover® and CashFlow CentralSM, with the industry-leading small business payroll and HR solution, RUN Powered by ADP®.
